Subject: [PATCH] feat: full i18n for the user section (EN/FR)

Wire ~45 user-facing components to react-i18next and add EN/FR
translations (~450 new keys). Pages now fully switch to French:
search/filters, event cards, auth, dashboard, bookmarks, registrations,
tickets, payments, profile, settings, notifications, interests,
recommendations, reports, about, organizers, legal, statistics, plus
shared navbar/footer/appshell/mobile nav. EN/FR in exact parity
(868 keys), 0 missing t() keys, build passes.
